quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,44,"Kaa a sikku won'de ko …ďuri heewde e ma…ď…ďe he…ďe nana ma he…ďe kakkila? Anndu kam…ďe …ďe ngonaani si wanaa wano neemoraa…ói, toode, ko kam…ďe …ďuri majjude laawol."
  25,45,"Kaa a tinaani fa'ade e Joomi maa…óa honno O fortiri …óowdi ndin? Sinndo O Muuyuno O wa…óatno ndi dee∆īundi, refti Min mba…ói na'ange ngen tinndinatnge e mayri."
  25,46,"refti Min tami ndi ka amen tamannde newiinde."
  25,47,"Ko Kako woni oon ba…óan…óo on jemma on koltu e …óoyngol ngol fooftere, O wa…ói √Īalama on ngal saakor…óo."
  25,48,"Ko KaŇčko woni On gaccitu…óo keni …óin ko …ói weltinooji hakkunde Yurmeende makko nden, Min njippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam laa…ď…óam."
  25,49,"Fii yo Min nguurnitir …óam leydi maayndi, Min njarrna…óam kadi kon ko Min tagi neemoraa…ói e yim…ďe …óuu…óu…ďe."
  25,50,"GooŇč…óii Min pennsitii nde hakkunde ma…ď…ďe fii yo …ďe mbaajito, salii …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen si wonaa jeddugol."
  25,51,"Sinndo min muuyuno min Nulatno e kala saare jeertinoowo."
  25,52,"Wota a …óofto yeddu…ďe …ďe ha…ď e ma…ď…ďe hare jihaadi mawnde."
  25,53,"Ko KaŇčko woni oon jillindir…óo maaje …óen …ói…ói, ngoo…óoo ko welngo ∆īem ngoo…óoo kadi ko haa…óngo tak, O wa…ói wirngallo hakkunde majje, e heedo heedaango."
  25,54,"Ko KaŇčko woni on Tak…óo …ďanndunke immorde e ndiyam …óam, O wa…ói mo dammbe e esiraawo, Joomi maa…óa laatike ko o kattan…óo."
  25,55,"He…ďe ndewa gah Alla kon ko nafataa …ďe lorrataa …ďe, jeddu…óo on laatike ko o tee…óii…óo Joomi makko."